{"tid":397504,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣，覺得同一種飲品，罐裝枝裝盒裝係會有分別......","createTime":"2017-09-12T14:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T05:05:39.000Z","uid":75100,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00b5482d874c972b22c75890064fa5ad309572b1","tid":397504,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:00:01.000Z","msg":"汽水黎講，枝裝七喜難飲到爆，好似糖水咁，但罐裝好飲d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雀巢檸茶黎講，罐裝 &gt;&gt;枝裝 &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;盒裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到底係咩道理? 定係我味覺有事，有無做過飲品廠既巴打分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516f3f9e91f42e06195bac36671bfead2805d913","tid":397504,"uid":9984,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:03:22.000Z","msg":"我都覺得罐裝可樂好飲過支裝<br />\n好似感覺上多氣D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81935e2eeb2c55aa85c2e1ab4cc9df8135b7d09","tid":397504,"uid":127770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:19:09.000Z","msg":"罐裝 &gt;枝裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔飲盒裝"},{"pid":"b5fa8fbb95e04da886d58068717c0cbb1cf8acb4","tid":397504,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:27:04.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得玻璃樽嘅鮮奶同維他奶係最好飲 <br />\n成日都好期待冬天出玻璃樽野飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n梳離咗題"},{"pid":"84fa602a528b78971e543ce54af26ff636f5a51c","tid":397504,"uid":145803,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:28:10.000Z","msg":"所有汽水 : 玻璃樽裝 &gt; 罐裝 &gt; 枝裝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97e3ca688b07efaa0c0f90b04166a8f6e1c99e0","tid":397504,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:30:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>硬係覺得玻璃樽嘅鮮奶同維他奶係最好飲 <br />\n成日都好期待冬天出玻璃樽野飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n梳離咗題</blockquote><br />\n細個有次去d污污槽槽既牛腩麵鋪，飲左d玻璃樽裝既汽水，之後腸胃炎柯到住係廁所咁制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自此唔敢再飲呢D循環回收的樽裝野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7886f174d8c10ed52fa393a4713e16f5b13b8c","tid":397504,"uid":129026,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:33:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>硬係覺得玻璃樽嘅鮮奶同維他奶係最好飲 <br />\n成日都好期待冬天出玻璃樽野飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n梳離咗題</blockquote><br />\n細個有次去d污污槽槽既牛腩麵鋪，飲左d玻璃樽裝既汽水，之後腸胃炎柯到住係廁所咁制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自此唔敢再飲呢D循環回收的樽裝野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解唔懷疑係碗麵問題呢"},{"pid":"598dcda27bdd59313abb6f0b675045555ce5814d","tid":397504,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:35:07.000Z","msg":"啤酒好似有唔同"},{"pid":"cfac45bd6973877ab357f2ecf3f03963f812c167","tid":397504,"uid":9809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:37:50.000Z","msg":"聽講玻璃樽嘅可樂同罐裝膠樽裝嘅可樂係兩間廠造<br />\n個人覺得玻璃樽裝好飲好多"},{"pid":"b7c7f2609ffe270eebdbc083b1001a6bef555e5b","tid":397504,"uid":75537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:40:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講玻璃樽嘅可樂同罐裝膠樽裝嘅可樂係兩間廠造<br />\n個人覺得玻璃樽裝好飲好多</blockquote><br />\n會唔會係可承受嘅二氧化碳壓力嘅關係"},{"pid":"b3ad46f246227c293489b6261498bd9c0404d53b","tid":397504,"uid":133256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:36:48.000Z","msg":"係溝左鋁，膠，紙既味道"},{"pid":"282ed376b68482e14fdbeed90e94982d691f7a47","tid":397504,"uid":46332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:41:37.000Z","msg":"用唔同size嘅飲管飲可樂都唔同味添"},{"pid":"7c33ee762893fb898017e9e074aa43a35